14. COMMUNITY DATASET

    The community dataset hosted at:
      https://huggingface.co/datasets/ray0rf1re/Site.scraped

    is community-contributed and subject to the following terms:

      a) The dataset maintainer (ray0rf1re / minerofthesoal) does NOT
         own, claim ownership of, or hold any rights to contributed
         content.

      b) All rights in contributed content remain exclusively with the
         Original Creators and rights holders.

      c) Contributors are solely responsible for ensuring they have the
         legal right to upload and share the content they contribute.
         By contributing, you represent and warrant that you have such
         rights.

      d) Contributors MUST NOT upload content that contains:
         (i)   Personal Data without a valid legal basis.
         (ii)  Content obtained in violation of Section 9 (Prohibited
               Uses).
         (iii) Content subject to confidentiality obligations.
         (iv)  Malware, malicious code, or deceptive content.

      e) Rights holders may request removal of their content via the
         GitHub issue tracker at:
         https://github.com/minerofthesoal/Scraper/issues

      f) Removal requests will be honored within a reasonable
         timeframe, not to exceed 30 calendar days from receipt of a
         valid request. Urgent requests involving Personal Data or
         safety concerns will be prioritized.

      g) The dataset is provided for research and educational purposes.
         Commercial use of individual records may require separate
         permission from Original Creators.

      h) The dataset maintainer reserves the right to remove any
         contribution that violates this license, applicable law, or
         community standards, without prior notice.

    >>> What this means in practice:
    >>> The community dataset is a shared resource. Nobody owns the
    >>> contributed content except the original creators. If your
    >>> content is in the dataset and you want it removed, open a
    >>> GitHub issue and it will be taken down within 30 days.

