=============================================================================

  v1.0 — Initial release.
  v2.0 — Added AI/ML provisions, community dataset terms, citations.
  v2.1 — Clarified AI/ML training provisions, added data retention and
         deletion obligations, improved international compatibility.
  v3.0 — Major revision. Added TL;DR summary, plain-language
         explanations throughout, data minimization requirements,
         prohibited uses (harassment, surveillance, deception),
         anti-scraping-as-a-service clause, explicit consent and
         ethical scraping guidelines, expanded international law
         coverage (GDPR, CCPA, PIPL, LGPD, POPIA, PDPA, APPI, etc.),
         termination provisions, and improved overall structure.

